        <abstract>
            <p>Is it fair to take advantage of knowing that Wallace is in the field? Seems hard on CD to lose priority of many years, but does not feel this alters justice of case.</p>
            <p>Baby [Charles Waring Darwin] has much fever. Frightened because three children in village have died from scarlet fever.</p>
        </abstract>
